*[[Tenor saxophone]] Concerto: [[Richard Rodney Bennett|Bennett]], [[Eric Ewazen|Ewazen]], [[Morton Gould|Gould]], [[Dimitri Nicolau|Nicolau]], [[Robert Ward (composer)|Ward]], [[Alec Wilder|Wilder]].
*[[Theremin]] concerto: [[Kalevi Aho|Aho]]
